{"tid":2501109,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：45個非政府組織促請東盟讓緬甸民選議員列席會議","createTime":"2021-04-23T06:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:53:38.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d38ccb703abe98685a7b38a725d92981ea82d6a","tid":2501109,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"東盟明日在印尼首都雅加達舉行峰會，討論緬甸局勢，緬甸國防軍總司令敏昂萊將會出席。<br />\n<br />\n45個東南亞國家的非政府組織發表聯署，要求東盟領袖讓被軍方罷免的緬甸民選議員列席，認為如果各國領袖不與緬甸民選的合法代表協商，峰會就不會在解決危機方面，取得任何成果，又說邀請敏昂萊出席會議，變相對軍政府向人民實施種族滅絕與屠殺，提供合法性。<br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼外長王毅較早時說，期待會議為緬甸局勢緩和降溫發揮建設作用，為緬甸局勢實現「軟著陸」開好頭，<strong>實現有利於推動緬甸國內政治和解、體現東盟建設性作用，避免域外的不當介入</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587342-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587342-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzqS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=61c2313b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587342-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=05682a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587342-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d949850e4f3dea7b2a48b42042f8acc7fd768cf4","tid":2501109,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"emergency summit有冇美國睇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}